# Privacy Policy for Universal Attachment Guard

Last updated: [Current Date]

## Data Collection
Universal Attachment Guard does NOT collect, store, or transmit any personal data or email content.

## How It Works
- All processing occurs locally in your browser
- No data is sent to external servers
- No tracking or analytics are performed
- No user accounts or profiles are created

## Permissions
The extension requires permissions to access email provider websites solely to:
- Detect email composition interfaces
- Analyze local email content for attachment keywords
- Display warning dialogs when needed

## Contact
For questions about this privacy policy, contact: [dev@cankatsarac.com]
